Class GAL_NumericalGeneConfig<T extends java.lang.Number & java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • JGAL.GAL_GeneConfig<T>
      • JGAL.GAL_NumericalGeneConfig<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GAL_DoubleGeneConfig, GAL_IntegerGeneConfig

    public abstract class GAL_NumericalGeneConfig<T extends java.lang.Number & java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends GAL_GeneConfig<T>
    The GAL_NumericalGeneConfig is an abstract class for the configuration of a GAL_Gene wich trait is a number

    Subclasses of GAL_NumericalGeneConfig must provide method for setRandomValueTo
